The '''''Agence Nationale de l'Aviation Civile et de la Météorologie de l'Union des Comores''''' ('''ANACM''' "National Civil Aviation and Meteorological Agency") is the civil aviation authority of the [[Comoros]]. It is also in charge of investigating aviation accidents and incidents.<ref>"[http://www.bea.aero/en/enquetes/flight.iy.626/flight.iy.626.php Flight IY 626 on 30 June 2009 A310-300, registerd{{sic}} 7O-ADJ]." [[Bureau d'Enquêtes et d'Analyses pour la Sécurité de l'Aviation Civile]]. Retrieved on 6 May 2011.</ref> Its head office is in [[Moroni, Comoros|Moroni]].<ref>"[http://www.ioc-tsunami.org/index.php?option=com_oe&task=viewInstitutionRecord&institutionID=13069 Agence Nationale de l’Aviation Civile et de la Météorologie]." [[Intergovernmental Oceanographic Commission]]. Retrieved on 26 May 2011.</ref>

