'''Bansa''' is a village in the [[Ga East Municipal District|Ga East Municipal district]], a [[Districts of Ghana|district]] in the [[Greater Accra Region]] of [[Ghana]].<ref name="Ga East Municipal District">[http://gaeast.ghanadistricts.gov.gh/?arrow=dnf&_=2&r=1&rlv=towns Ga East Municipal District] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040306/http://gaeast.ghanadistricts.gov.gh/?arrow=dnf&_=2&r=1&rlv=towns |date=March 4, 2016 }}</ref>
==Village structure== The village is under the jurisdiction of the [[Ga East Municipal District]] and is in the [[Abokobi-Madina (Ghana parliament constituency)|Abokobi-Madina constituency]] of the [[Ghana Parliament|Ghana parliament]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://library.fes.de/pdf-files/bueros/ghana/03610.pdf |title=Elections 2004. Ghana's Parliamentary and Presidential Elections|accessdate=2011-06-13 |pages=11 |publisher=[[Electoral Commission of Ghana]]| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110522115353/http://library.fes.de/pdf-files/bueros/ghana/03610.pdf| archivedate= 22 May 2011 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>
