'''Portugal''' participated in the '''Eurovision Song Contest 1998''' in [[Birmingham]].   [[Alma Lusa]] represented Portugal with the song "[[Se eu te pudesse abracar]]". They scored 36 points (highest 10 from France) placing 12th.

