[[File:Research Library in Olomouc.jpg|thumbnail|right|Research Library in Olomouc]]
The '''Research Library in Olomouc''' ([[Czech language|Czech]]: ''Vědecká knihovna v Olomouci'') is a public library in [[Olomouc]], [[Czech Republic]].

The library was established in 1566 by the Olomouc college and served until 1860 as '''[[Palacký_University_of_Olomouc#University_Library|University of Olomouc Library]]'''.

Nowadays it is one of the largest libraries in the Czech Republic with unique collection of historical sources, among others 1451 [[manuscript]]s and 1700 [[incunable]]s.

